        <h1 class="acl-title">Indonesia — AI Copyright Law</h1>
        <p class="acl-excerpt">Indonesia's copyright framework is currently adapting to the rapid adoption of AI, relying heavily on traditional human authorship requirements while developing new digital economy guidelines.</p>
